reviewText: Beautiful visual trip in the oceans!
All three of these movies are wonderful and entertaining but in a good way.....soft and relaxing...just like I like them!
I have gotten many of the other nature programs, this one was disappointing.  It is best for children or people with little nature background. I watched it once and that is it.
This bluray ocean 3 pack worth every penny ! Beautiful scenery and excellent picture quality plus lovely soundtrack,Imax at its best ! Go get it, Im sure u won't regret !
